          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Boost your brand’s visibility and connect with your audience with our premium Custom Stickers and Custom Vinyl Magnets. Whether you’re building brand recognition, promoting an event, or expressing creativity, our customizable products deliver professional results.</p><h4><strong>Why Choose Our Custom Stickers & Vinyl Magnets?</strong></h4><p><strong>High-Quality Materials</strong></p><p>Our custom stickers are made from durable vinyl with over two years of outdoor durability, while our vinyl magnets are crafted from weather-resistant magnetic material perfect for vehicles, storefronts, fridges, toolboxes, and more.<br/><br/><strong>Vibrant, Full-Color Printing</strong></p><p>Every sticker and magnet is produced using advanced printing technology to ensure crisp detail and bold, accurate colors that bring your artwork or brand to life.<br/><br/><strong>Weatherproof and Fade-Resistant</strong></p><p>Both our vinyl stickers and magnets are built to endure the elements. Stickers are UV-protected, waterproof, and even dishwasher safe—ideal for bottles, helmets, laptops, and packaging. Vinyl magnets are designed to handle outdoor exposure without cracking, peeling, or fading.<br/><br/><strong>Easy Application and Removal</strong></p><p>Our stickers apply smoothly and peel away clean with no sticky residue left behind. Vinyl magnets can be placed, removed, and repositioned instantly, offering a reusable and damage-free branding solution.</p>",
            "text_size": "regular"
          }
        }
      },
