            "question": "What is the minimum order quantity?",
            "answer": "<p>Minimum order quantity varies depending on type. For standard custom stickers, the MOQ is 100 pieces. For bumper and truck stickers, their minimum order quantities are 50 and 4 respectively. Magnets carry an MOQ of 20 pieces.</p>",
