          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I see a proof before final printing?",
            "answer": "<p>We do not currently offer proofs for custom stickers or magnets. We do, however, offer it for our <a href=\"/pages/shop-custom-patches\" title=\"Shop Patch Types\">custom patches</a>.</p>",
